				<td colspan="2"><span>Personally I am heartened by them pushing the patch back.  The track record on patches to fix patches speak volumes.  This at least shows they are not only using our feedback to make the game better, but also learning from their own mistakes (not saying who's mistake, mind you).
<br />

<br />
Yes, I was anxiously awaiting the patch like most everyone else, but I am more than willing to wait another week, or another two weeks if that winds up being decided, in order to have sufficient testing done.  While this doesn't mean there won't be a patch after the patch, it does hold the possible meaning that there won't be additional patches after that.  Complicated code is complicated code, and sometimes things happen.  It shows an attitude change somewhere within SOE at least from the previous patching code to the live servers that was repeated bug reported as broken on test.
<br />

<br />
Thanks SOE....
<br />

